description:
I promise to protect you always. ⁣
⁣
I promise you will know what my eyes look like, my nose, my mouth, my kisses.⁣
⁣
I promise that even when it seems like we are the underdog, I will fight for you till we win.⁣
⁣
I promise to do whatever I can to fill your days full of laughter and sunshine. ⁣
⁣
I promise to give you every opportunity in the world that I can. ⁣
⁣
I promise that in times of darkness, I will do whatever I can to help you experience light. ⁣
⁣
You will always know my love. ⁣
⁣
Xo mama⁣
